bilingual.source: Prospective employers like to see what you have written.
bilingual.target: 未来的老板愿意看你所写过的东西。

bilingual.source: Do look a prospective employer in the eye while speaking.
bilingual.target: 说话的时候要把面试官看作你未来的老板.

bilingual.source: And judging prospective saleswomen by their looks was company policy.
bilingual.target: 公司还有一项政策就是从外表判断未来的女销售员.

bilingual.source: The prospective inspector prospected his prospect with his own perspective.
bilingual.target: 未来的检查员用自己的观点勘察他的前景.

bilingual.source: Loans are a bit easier to come by for prospective homebuyers.
bilingual.target: 对于未来的购房者来说,贷款会多少容易一些了.

bilingual.source: The prospective inspector prospected his prospect with his own perspective .
bilingual.target: 未来的检查员用自己的观点勘察的他的前景。

bilingual.source: She says any face time with new people can turn into a prospective business deal.
bilingual.target: 她说,任何同新鲜面孔打交道的机会都有可能转化为未来的商业交易.

bilingual.source: Do you really want a prospective boss checking what you used to do at the weekends?
bilingual.target: 你是否希望未来的老板通过浏览页面，看到你周末干了什么?。

bilingual.source: Penguins mate for life, and they propose by giving their prospective mate a pebble.
bilingual.target: 企鹅有终生的配偶，而且他们是通过一枚鹅卵石向未来的伴侣求婚的。

bilingual.source: If a prospective employer conducts a background check and discovers that kissgood - bye.
bilingual.target: 要是未来的老板做背景调查时发现真相,那只有拜拜了.

list.abstract: Prospective是一个英语单词，是预期的的意思。

yingyinNormal.en: So, Bernadette, how's the wedding planning going? And I'm not asking as a prospective bridesmaid. Pick me! Pick me!
yingyinNormal.zh: 伯纳黛特，婚礼筹划得怎样了？我这么问可不是想成为伴娘候选人哦。快选我吧！选我吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Do you mislead prospective students? No. We're not allowed to. We're subject to the same laws every business must follow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们是否误导了一些有希望的学生？没有，那样的行为是被禁止的，我们遵守每一条相关的法律法规。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 预期的；盼望中的；未来的；未来可能发生的

word_family.mean: n. 未来事件发生的可能性；可能成功的人；潜在主顾；潜在客户；潜在矿藏或矿床；景象；景色；视野；前景；展望

sense_info_list.en: (of a person) expected or expecting to be something particular in the future

examination_example.sentence: Persuading <highlight>prospective</highlight> fathers to consider a change in their career.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 说服准爸爸们考虑改变职业生涯。

examination_example.sentence: Taking measures to attract <highlight>prospective</highlight> male teachers to work in the field.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 采取措施吸引有意向的男教师到这一领域工作。

sense_info_list.en: of or concerned with or related to the future

examination_example.sentence: If you do several jobs in a relatively short span of time, <highlight>prospective</highlight> employers might perceive that you lack loyalty.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在相对较短的时间内做了几份工作，潜在的雇主可能会认为你缺乏忠诚度。
